This paper is primarily focused on distributed deep learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the communication overhead and optimization techniques, which are relevant to distributed computing (cs.DC) and distributed systems (cs.DS). The proposed algorithm and analysis are related to neural networks (cs.NE) and computer vision (cs.CV).
